{"tid":1259061,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"得罪講句，比你拎夠立法會2/3席都係無用","createTime":"2019-06-26T12:08:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-26T12:12:04.000Z","uid":122994,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4bf680417621c33c573563885d54c8f523d25e0c","tid":1259061,"uid":122994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T12:08:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大家唔好唔記得香港係行政主導，基本法規定立法會只有同意權無立法/創制權，議員提既議案無約束力，即係廢<br />\n<br />\n泛民從來唔會raise out呢個issue。美帝個民主人權法案話2020普選立會，但完全無提立會既功能問題呢點，大家可以理解為美帝係向習總提出要共治香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，即係中共做事，美帝同意<br />\n<br />\n咁立會拎到半數叫唔叫有民主呀？無囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n拎到全部又有無呀？都係無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為人民想立既法依然立唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n講咁多野都係想提下大家，咩立會過半當係一次性抗爭就好啦。應該可以擋一擋明日大愚同高鐵B段既，如果泛民唔出賣既話<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n記住真正既民主只有重寫基本法/制憲先可以有，大家唔好比泛民打手同選舉撚帶到失焦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地要準備既係全面執政，香港起碼有實然主權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以讀緊書既讀好d書，識兩文三語既學夠三文五語，第日做外交官同香港大使<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7757a7fa69caa181d91c77f335029d31c32e193b","tid":1259061,"uid":122994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T12:09:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"151ada4817cab551692f44b004aab96959432c59","tid":1259061,"uid":122994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"